{"tid":1280060,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"如果大家驚既灰既請諗諗梁天琦，相信自己相信同路人！","createTime":"2019-07-03T00:15:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T13:40:37.000Z","uid":10287,"like":119,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e8b6db1b6dcd7fb248206d8cd3b4c47f4668444f","tid":1280060,"uid":10287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T00:15:10.000Z","msg":"我知大家唔開心 無力感好重 好灰<br />\n白色恐佈 驚俾人捉<br />\n但係有一樣野係梁天琦帶俾我地<br />\n要相信自己 相信自己所相信既野 要相信同路人<br />\n天琦去到外國讀書大可以一走了之 唔返香港坐唔應該坐既監 背負住咁大既包袱<br />\n<br />\n梁天琦佢無放棄到 無走左去 佢返左黎香港面對<br />\n我唔知天琦佢心入面怕唔怕 但係就算係怕 係驚 係灰<br />\n都希望大家唔好放棄自己 <br />\n除左不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰 不譴責<br />\n最緊要係 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不放棄！！</span></span><br />\n堅定自己立場 守住依一關"},{"pid":"c927948808af8232624df943d34b1bb9b04a5c8f","tid":1280060,"uid":10287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T00:17:18.000Z","msg":"岩岩起身見到有手足心情唔好 想做傻事<br />\n無時間排版再睇下有冇打錯字"},{"pid":"a238780f419c5c867eb8eb4d2f5e39975fb53c19","tid":1280060,"uid":10287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T00:18:17.000Z","msg":"唔好放棄呀大家"},{"pid":"243ea6b75488f8f5771f419724d5e62baa97bf3e","tid":1280060,"uid":10287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T00:19:44.000Z","msg":"記住一齊黎 一齊走呀"},{"pid":"977349e81877f0a8126bd6449be1dea351176e49","tid":1280060,"uid":10287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T00:21:39.000Z","msg":"人手推"},{"pid":"5e1ab834e2a3f79d15cf6d163f6d927423c16741","tid":1280060,"uid":10287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T00:24:36.000Z","msg":"加油呀"},{"pid":"98aca2f0a74506010415733f2218790f956b3920","tid":1280060,"uid":10287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T00:26:35.000Z","msg":"不放棄！"},{"pid":"5d571221a79c17d7fd36f8501b07e5ec1c26a3bc","tid":1280060,"uid":10287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T00:30:32.000Z","msg":"不放棄！"},{"pid":"3